# ==========================================================================
# iHymns — Shared Setlist JSON Storage
#
# This directory stores server-side shared setlist JSON files created
# via the Share Set List feature (#155). Files are created and read
# exclusively by PHP (api.php) — never served directly.
#
# SECURITY: This directory is outside the public web root, but this
# .htaccess provides defence-in-depth in case of misconfiguration.
# ==========================================================================

# Deny all direct access
Deny from all
